Setting in 24 hours after Joe slamming D’s car door shut, Part 2 continues telling the story. Of Joe and D, who still have a lot to work out (for themselves and between each other) and also of Jack and Sarah.Is D really going to join Pete for his party at work? What about her scheduled trip to London? And the job she applied for? How is Joe dealing with what she told him? Is he going to let Liz get away with what she did? Are Jack and Sarah going to get involved in all this? And what about the woman Jack’s secretly in love with?_For everyone who has outgrown young adult by a few years but still likes a good, realistic story (that’s not only a love story) about people like you and I - taking place in Europe.Check http://www.billywoodsmith.com as well.